<h2 class="title">EPA NESHAP for Plating and Polishing Operations: Final Rule Effective July 1, 2010</h2> 
</div>


Midwest Air Products offers a quick and cost-effective solution for compliance with this rule. The MistMaster composite mesh pad is available in a vertical or horizontal configuration. The MistMaster can be easily installed in an existing exhaust system and removes 99 percent of plating bath particulate. Platers, call Mapco today. <br>
